
This code accompanies the Dreamforce 2012 presentation "Using Force.com to automate established business processes".

It contains example force.com apex controllers, visualforce pages, and a custom object that enable developers to create a regenerating scheduled job and Esker Fax on Demand API integration.

If you have any queries, please get in touch via email (chris.lewis@desynit.com)

*prerequisites*

In order to install the related code, you will need a developer sandbox or developer org (for free at www.developerforce.com).

If you want to communicate with Esker fax web services, you will need an Esker fax account, for more information please contact an Esker representative or visit www.Esker.com .

